These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, epic, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, trike, quad-bike
1. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
4. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | thriller | epic    |
| Transport     | trike    | quad-bike       | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, mechanic, musician
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, sailing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the musician is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
4. the mechanic is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | musician | dancer | mechanic  |
| Sport   | swimming  | surfing  | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, pilot, architect
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, salsa, house
1. the fan of salsa is on the far left or far right##3
2. the teacher is on the far right##1
3. the pilot is the fan of house##1
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | architect | pilot | teacher |
| Music-Genre   | trance        | house    | salsa        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, drawing
3 different pets are kept: bird, snake, pony
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
3. the owner of the bird is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | drawing | gardening | sudoku |
| Pet     | snake  | bird    | pony  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | mystery | thriller |
| Transport     | airplane   | snowmobile   | tram   |

