.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, pop, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, mexican, argentine
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the argentine is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | hip-hop    | metal       |
| Nationality   | mexican | argentine | spanish |

