.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, strawberry, onion
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda        | coffee  | almond-milk   |
| Food       | onion | strawberry | cranberry |

