.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, polish, japanese
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, goldfish
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
2. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | italian | japanese | polish |
| Pet           | pony    | goldfish    | guinea-pig       |

