2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | magic-tricks   | singing |
| Sport   | cycling | weightlifting | handball |

