.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, almond-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, time-travel
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | soy-milk | juice         |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | disaster  | zombie |

 